OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy,
OL,6,Fperhaps with the odd spot of drizzle.
OL,7,FDry this afternoon with the chance
OL,8,Fsome brightness breaking through, more
OL,9,Fespecially Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry,
OL,12,Fperhaps a little brightness across
OL,13,FOrkney. Then the rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill be mainly dry although some low
OL,15,Fcloud around.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FDry with variable amounts
OL,18,Fof cloud, some sunshine likely to
OL,19,Fbreak through at times. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
