OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying largely dry and settled
OL,7,Falthough a fair amount of cloud around
OL,8,Fat times. Some brighter spells too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
